即另以\r\n書狀向簡易法庭陳述或請求傳訊。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c2703%2c20220915%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,簡,2703,20220915,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"2703","JDATE":"20220915","JTITLE":"傷害"}